title: Regular Classes
highlightText: We conduct daily yoga and meditation classes
description: Reach out to us if you are looking for personal consultations, counselling sessions & initiation into meditation by Santhi. Santhi will attend to your requests on appointment basis. Want to host us?Interested in spreading the wisdom of Santhis teachings? Santhi travels to Europe twice a year and spends the rest of his time mostly in India.Contact us for more information about his availability & to schedule seminars, workshops, satsangs and other customized programs in your place of request.
